# AI-BOS SaaS Binding (web/)

When working under `web/`, treat the delivery project as **`PRJ-SAAS-GROWRIXOS-001`**.

## Mandatory

1. Read `AI-BOS/project-registry/registry.json` entry `PRJ-SAAS-GROWRIXOS-001` before material changes.
2. Consume declared Knowledge Object IDs (not chat summaries) — at minimum as scoped by the active delivery skill’s `references/ai-bos-binding.md`.
3. Prefer AI-BOS KOs as SSOT when they exist; `DOC/Universal/` remains reference only.
4. Follow `WF-DLV-SAAS-FEATURE-001` for feature delivery; use `ST-TST-001` / phase-end enforcers at gates.
5. Record evidence in `DOC/PROJECT PLAN/Tasks/tasks.md`.

